
INSTALL EXTENSION

Dependency

jquery mobile
http://jquerymobile.com/

* get extension from github
* place it in your /extension directory or /ezpublish_legacy/extension
* enable extension globally in settings/override/site.ini.append.php
    [ExtensionSettings]
    ActiveExtensions[]=xrowslideshow

    * or per siteaccess in settings/siteaccess/<your_siteaccess_name>/site.ini.append.php
        [ExtensionSettings]
        ActiveAccessExtensions[]=xrowslideshow

* design "standard" needs to be enabled for your siteaccess design.ini.append.php
* clear caches

OPTIONAL

* enable xrowslideshow_responsive.css in your settings/.../design.ini.append.php for responsive behavior

GETTING STARTED

Example for implementing slideshow in JS:
* xrowslideshow/design/standard/javascript/xrowslideshow.example.js

Example template with HTML-Markup:
* xrowslideshow/design/standard/templates/example_template.tpl